28:00.613 --> 28:02.346
This is our time.

28:02.348 --> 28:05.883
♪ mother and child ♪

28:05.885 --> 28:07.384
Did she beg?

28:07.386 --> 28:09.053
What?

28:09.055 --> 28:09.953
Elise,
when you killed her.

28:09.955 --> 28:12.122
That was on you, jake.

28:12.124 --> 28:13.691
You promised me you would
take care of olivia.

28:13.693 --> 28:14.858
Remember?

28:14.860 --> 28:16.226
Look where she ended up.

28:16.228 --> 28:19.029
Huck: You shouldn't have
mentioned my family.

28:19.031 --> 28:21.565
This was a test for<i> you.</i>

28:21.567 --> 28:23.567
It was never about me.
It's about you.

28:23.569 --> 28:25.569
You're an addict.
You think you're recovered,

28:25.571 --> 28:27.971
But you wouldn't know for sure
until you tempted yourself,

28:27.973 --> 28:30.407
Until you stared the drugs
in the face.

28:30.409 --> 28:32.876
I was the drug --
the ultimate trigger.

28:32.878 --> 28:34.511
You passed, I'm breathing,

28:34.513 --> 28:36.680
And now you think you're ready
to have the one thing

28:36.682 --> 28:39.983
In your life that completes
you -- your family!

28:44.590 --> 28:46.256
I'm going home.

28:46.258 --> 28:48.025
Mm. Sad.

28:48.027 --> 28:50.761
Predictable.

28:56.035 --> 29:00.070
Family is the only thing
that has kept you alive here.

29:02.875 --> 29:08.245
Olivia is the only reason
that you're alive.

29:08.247 --> 29:10.347
She's also the reason
I'm shackled to this chair.

29:10.349 --> 29:13.083
Family is a burden.

29:13.085 --> 29:15.552
We're brothers.

29:15.554 --> 29:19.056
After all we've been through,
all we've seen...

29:19.058 --> 29:20.858
We won't let --
[ gunshot ]

29:24.864 --> 29:30.367
Rowan: A pressure point,
soft tissue, an illness,

29:30.369 --> 29:33.604
An antidote to greatness.

29:33.606 --> 29:36.607
You think you're better off
with people who rely on you,

29:36.609 --> 29:38.709
Depend on you,
but you're wrong,

29:38.711 --> 29:41.245
Because you will inevitably
end up needing them,

29:41.247 --> 29:44.815
Which makes you weak,
pliable.

29:44.817 --> 29:47.084
Family doesn't complete you.

29:47.086 --> 29:50.921
It destroys you.

29:50.923 --> 29:59.129
♪ heavenly hosts
sing alleluia ♪

30:09.642 --> 30:11.208
Liv?

30:20.019 --> 30:22.719
You want to tell me
what's going on?

30:25.324 --> 30:27.691
Where were you tonight?

30:27.693 --> 30:29.159
Olivia...

30:31.664 --> 30:32.629
What the hell are you --

30:32.631 --> 30:34.565
Yes! Oh, thank you.

30:36.468 --> 30:39.002
You can't be serious.

30:41.307 --> 30:43.640
Olivia, I am trying
to talk to you!

30:43.642 --> 30:45.108
I<i> tried</i> tonight

30:45.110 --> 30:46.276
To make it to your dinner.

30:46.278 --> 30:47.878
I thought I'd get back
in time.

30:47.880 --> 30:51.548
I really...Tried, but...

30:53.118 --> 30:54.618
But what?

31:05.364 --> 31:06.964
Where were you, olivia?

31:08.701 --> 31:10.400
Something came up --

31:10.402 --> 31:11.902
Do not lie to me!

31:16.508 --> 31:18.242
I don't know
what you want me to --

31:18.244 --> 31:22.045
You were running.
That's what I want you to say.

31:22.047 --> 31:23.814
That's what
I want you to admit.

31:23.816 --> 31:28.518
It doesn't really matter
where you were tonight.

31:28.520 --> 31:32.022
You just weren't here.

31:32.024 --> 31:33.991
You didn't make it to that
dinner tonight because --

31:33.993 --> 31:35.926
Because I didn't
want to go.

31:35.928 --> 31:38.595
Why would I, fitz?

31:38.597 --> 31:41.098
So I could sit in the corner
with the other housewives

31:41.100 --> 31:43.200
And force myself
to watch you run

31:43.202 --> 31:45.102
With the big dogs
across the room?

31:45.104 --> 31:48.272
Guess what -- I am a big dog,
so I didn't want to go.

31:48.274 --> 31:49.740
I knew this was
gonna happen.

31:49.742 --> 31:51.275
I knew when
I moved you in here

31:51.277 --> 31:53.410
And tried to give us a real shot
at making this work --

31:53.412 --> 31:55.078
You mean when
you moved me in here

31:55.080 --> 31:58.015
And treated me like I was
some kind of hostage?

31:58.017 --> 31:59.917
Is that honestly
what you think?

31:59.919 --> 32:03.120
That all this is some kind of
sick, twisted punishment?

32:03.122 --> 32:04.588
Yes, I do.

32:04.590 --> 32:06.390
"punishment"?
What are you --
for my father.

32:06.392 --> 32:08.292
This has nothing
to do with --

32:08.294 --> 32:09.927
It has everything to do
with him.

32:09.929 --> 32:11.862
I get my father released,
I try to help you,

32:11.864 --> 32:13.463
I try to<i> save</i> you --

32:13.465 --> 32:17.067
Oh, let's not pretend you did
that for me, olivia.

32:17.069 --> 32:19.803
<i> That</i> was for<i> you.</i>

32:19.805 --> 32:22.439
You did that so you wouldn't
have to marry me.

32:26.812 --> 32:29.913
[ chuckles ]

32:29.915 --> 32:32.616
What was worse
for you, fitz?

32:32.618 --> 32:34.484
When I let my father go,

32:34.486 --> 32:37.421
Or when I asked you
not to kill him?

32:37.423 --> 32:40.057
Do I owe you now, fitz?

32:40.059 --> 32:43.060
Do I get to show
how worthy I am

32:43.062 --> 32:44.895
Of your sacrifices now,
fitz?

32:44.897 --> 32:48.065
Do I get to talk to wives
at cocktail parties for you?

32:48.067 --> 32:51.001
Trade recipes for you?
Plan dinners for you?

32:51.003 --> 32:56.239
Live in this cage for you,
and not breathe for you?!

32:56.241 --> 32:58.675
Tell me,
what must I do to prove

32:58.677 --> 33:02.079
I am forever indebted to you
for saving my father's life?!

33:02.081 --> 33:04.247
Olivia --
be your housewife?

33:04.249 --> 33:06.550
Your girlfriend?
Your property?!

33:10.489 --> 33:11.521
You stand there,

33:11.523 --> 33:13.323
And you think

33:13.325 --> 33:15.325
About what I have
been doing --

33:15.327 --> 33:18.662
And about everything
I have ever told you --

33:18.664 --> 33:22.733
And you tell me
who wouldn't run.

33:24.503 --> 33:27.237
Try to understand
what I am telling you.

33:28.841 --> 33:31.274
Moving you in here,

33:31.276 --> 33:33.377
Asking you
to go all-in on us --

33:33.379 --> 33:36.513
Oh, who is really lying
to who here, fitz?

33:36.515 --> 33:38.015
You asked me?

33:38.017 --> 33:40.217
When did you ask me?
When I tried to propose.

33:40.219 --> 33:41.551
When we were out
on the truman,

33:41.553 --> 33:42.686
When you
flat-out refused --

33:42.688 --> 33:44.454
That wasn't a proposal.

33:44.456 --> 33:46.356
That was manipulation.

33:46.358 --> 33:48.525
You want to talk
about manipulation?

33:48.527 --> 33:49.659
You think I don't know

33:49.661 --> 33:51.695
What you've been doing
this entire time?

33:51.697 --> 33:53.797
What are you
talking about?
I'm talking about<i> you...</i>

33:53.799 --> 33:54.965
Strutting around here,

33:54.967 --> 33:57.134
Wielding your
undue influence

33:57.136 --> 33:59.903
In your power capes
like you run the damn place.

33:59.905 --> 34:01.738
So you're bitter.
Is that it?

34:01.740 --> 34:04.041
After realizing how ineffectual
you actually are --

34:04.043 --> 34:05.742
You know,
you're worse than her.

34:05.744 --> 34:07.744
You're worse than mellie.

34:07.746 --> 34:09.079
At least with mellie,

34:09.081 --> 34:10.847
I knew what she was
the entire time.

34:10.849 --> 34:12.249
Unlike you.

34:12.251 --> 34:13.483
I mean, I knew where
you came from, but --

34:13.485 --> 34:15.185
Where I<i> came</i> from?

34:15.187 --> 34:17.654
We both know
who your father is.

34:17.656 --> 34:20.824
I came from a palace compared
to the man that raised you.

34:20.826 --> 34:22.659
At least my father
loved me.

34:22.661 --> 34:24.761
You want to know
who wouldn't run?

34:24.763 --> 34:26.930
Someone capable of being
in a relationship.

34:26.932 --> 34:28.899
Someone capable
of being normal.

34:28.901 --> 34:31.234
If you were someone
capable of being alone,

34:31.236 --> 34:34.004
Someone capable of
not suffocating me --

34:34.006 --> 34:36.106
I wasn't suffocating!
I was trying to show you --

34:36.108 --> 34:37.874
You were trying
to save me!

34:37.876 --> 34:39.609
I was trying to save us!

34:39.611 --> 34:41.745
There is no us!

34:41.747 --> 34:43.180
There is no this!

34:43.182 --> 34:46.016
There is no vermont!
There is no jam!

34:46.018 --> 34:48.952
There is no future!

34:48.954 --> 34:51.855
[ crying ]
not anymore.

35:11.777 --> 35:14.544
You just needed time...

35:17.416 --> 35:20.117
...To get used to the way
things work around here,

35:20.119 --> 35:24.454
The way things work with us
in here, to be here.

35:24.456 --> 35:27.390
You needed time.

35:27.392 --> 35:30.494
We didn't get any time.

35:33.765 --> 35:38.568
I told you, if it got out,
if they knew...

35:40.139 --> 35:43.840
We needed time before.

35:43.842 --> 35:47.277
We never had a chance.

35:47.279 --> 35:49.246
I told you.

35:50.516 --> 35:52.315
Before.

35:52.317 --> 35:55.318
If we're already broken
going in, then --

35:55.320 --> 35:57.087
I was unavailable before.

35:59.858 --> 36:02.859
You liked me unavailable.

36:09.201 --> 36:10.400
[ sighs ]

36:14.039 --> 36:16.706
I don't know you
available.

36:18.777 --> 36:21.711
She got this side of you.

36:21.713 --> 36:24.714
She did this part.

36:24.716 --> 36:26.883
I didn't have to.

36:30.122 --> 36:33.356
I didn't have
to be everything.

36:37.796 --> 36:40.697
You could've had
something...

36:40.699 --> 36:42.098
Been something.

36:46.071 --> 36:48.972
Mellie --
that's what she said.

37:10.262 --> 37:11.628
[ sniffles ]

37:23.041 --> 37:25.108
[ sighs ]

37:35.420 --> 37:37.320
Ugh.

37:41.193 --> 37:43.426
I hate that
you're always right.

37:47.132 --> 37:49.432
Me too.

37:49.434 --> 37:51.801
♪♪

37:54.740 --> 37:56.239
We tried.

37:56.241 --> 37:59.876
♪♪

37:59.878 --> 38:02.479
We did.

38:02.481 --> 38:05.782
♪♪

38:05.784 --> 38:14.891
♪ ave maria ♪

38:14.893 --> 38:16.660
No sign of huck.

38:16.662 --> 38:19.262
Looks like it's gonna be
just you and me tonight.

38:19.264 --> 38:22.299
Oh. I can't.
I was just about to take off.

38:22.301 --> 38:25.235
Where are you going?
My aunt sylvia's.

38:25.237 --> 38:27.103
She makes a great
sweet potato pie.

38:27.105 --> 38:30.473
Oh. Right.
Yeah, you have a family.

38:30.475 --> 38:32.742
Want to come?
No.

38:32.744 --> 38:33.677
I totally have plans.

38:33.679 --> 38:37.080
Merry christmas, quinn.

38:39.318 --> 38:41.785
Merry christmas, marcus.

38:41.787 --> 38:44.754
♪ ave... ♪

38:44.756 --> 38:46.156
The lid is on.

38:46.158 --> 38:47.624
There's no briefing
tomorrow.

38:47.626 --> 38:49.326
I don't want to get a call,
an e-mail, or a text --

38:49.328 --> 38:50.994
Abby.

38:53.665 --> 39:02.138
♪ benedicta tu in mulieribus ♪

39:02.140 --> 39:04.207
Sam, get me phil jurik
at<i> the post.</i>

39:04.209 --> 39:06.176
Oh.

39:06.178 --> 39:08.144
Wow.

39:08.146 --> 39:10.146
I see you wear scarves
sometimes,

39:10.148 --> 39:11.948
And, well,
I can see why.

39:11.950 --> 39:13.783
I mean, that neck --
it's epic.

39:13.785 --> 39:15.318
I wish I could
pull off a scarf,

39:15.320 --> 39:17.187
But I have nowhere near
the neck real estate you do.

39:20.359 --> 39:22.625
Oh, you hate it,
don't you?

39:22.627 --> 39:24.961
No. I love it.

39:24.963 --> 39:26.229
It's beautiful.
Really?

39:26.231 --> 39:27.864
You have great taste.

39:27.866 --> 39:30.233
I mean, your bracelet
is gorgeous.

39:30.235 --> 39:32.736
David rosen
gave it to me.

39:32.738 --> 39:40.210
♪ ave maria ♪

39:40.212 --> 39:41.211
Merry christmas.

39:45.384 --> 39:46.750
[ engine turns over ]

39:46.752 --> 39:50.186
♪♪

39:50.188 --> 39:52.422
Jake: You were right.

39:52.424 --> 39:54.724
It's hard to believe,
but...

39:54.726 --> 39:57.327
You were right.
Lazarus wasn't you.

39:57.329 --> 40:00.930
♪♪

40:00.932 --> 40:03.833
Jake.

40:07.539 --> 40:09.539
Welcome home, son.

40:09.541 --> 40:15.879
♪ ave maria ♪

40:15.881 --> 40:18.148
[ phone rings ]

40:20.519 --> 40:22.252
Hey.

40:22.254 --> 40:24.421
Come on up.

40:24.423 --> 40:28.024
♪♪

40:34.566 --> 40:37.333
♪♪

40:50.382 --> 40:52.715
[ knock on door ]

40:54.719 --> 40:56.119
Can you believe
the hardware store

40:56.121 --> 40:57.320
Just leaves this stuff outside
during the holidays?

40:57.322 --> 40:59.589
Did you shoplift
christmas?

40:59.591 --> 41:01.558
It was going in the bargain bin
tomorrow anyway.

41:01.560 --> 41:03.960
So, is there room
at the inn or what?

41:09.000 --> 41:12.035
♪♪

41:17.943 --> 41:19.075
[ elevator bell dings ]

41:21.913 --> 41:24.781
Inside, straight ahead.

41:24.783 --> 41:29.085
♪ benedicta tu in mulieribus ♪

41:29.087 --> 41:37.827
♪ et benedictus ♪

41:37.829 --> 41:46.135
♪ et benedictus
fructus ventris ♪

41:46.137 --> 41:55.545
♪ ventris tui, jesus ♪

41:55.547 --> 42:09.626
♪ ave maria ♪

42:12.197 --> 42:15.798
♪♪

42:22.574 --> 42:24.707
[<i> camera shutter clicking</i> ]
